title: 23/9 and I haven't received my 10years gift yet
body: My questios is... will I really get the 10years gift? I played on 13th September.

replies.body: The deadline for games was the 19th, so you'll be fine.  There are a lot of accounts to gift so it will take time to get to everybody per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight!

You will get the gifts, don't worry. They are sending them out piece by piece. If you haven't received your gifts at the end of the 23th I recommend you send a ticket to Riot Support. For more information check out this article: 

http://boards.euw.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support-en/GYljUrE4-ongoing-10-year-anniversary-gifts-are-still-being-given-out

I hope you'll receive your gifts ASAP :)
Ok thank you for your help :)
